53945.「装備品の 装備可能レベルが高いほど\n また 錬金効果が たくさんついているほ:
The higher the equipment's required level and the more alchemy effects it has, the more gems that can be extracted.
If the alchemy effects on the equipment are of good quality, the number of gems you can extract will increase even further.
Even if the equipment has a high quality itself, the number of gems will remain the same if it has no alchemy effects.
It's beneficial to add effects to equipment you plan on extracting from, since the amount of gems will increase, adding more value.

However, you may only extract gems from heavily used equipment against monsters of equal or greater strength.

53947.「使い込み度とは\n 装備品をどれくらい使い込んだのか\n 知るための 数値です:
An equipment's Usage Level indicates how much you have used a particular piece of equipment in battles.
After battling monsters of an equal or greater challenge to you, your equipment may sparkle, signifying its Usage Level has increased.
Once the Usage Level reaches 100, you will be able to extract Sweat & Tears Gems from it.
If you want to see an equipment's current Usage Level, you can view by examining its details.

60566.「装備品の 装備可能レベルが高いほど\n また 錬金効果が たくさんついているほ:
The higher the equipment's required level and the more alchemy effects it has, the more gems that can be extracted.
If the alchemy effects on the equipment are of good quality, the number of gems you can extract will increase even further.
Even if the equipment has a high quality itself, the number of gems will remain the same if it has no alchemy effects.
It's beneficial to add effects to equipment you plan on extracting from, since the amount of gems will increase, adding more value.

60567.「結晶を取りだすとは お使いの装備品から\n 職人仕事で使える新素材 汗と涙の結:
Gem extraction is a service that allows you to extract Sweat & Tears Gems from equipment, which can be used as crafting materials.
However, you may only extract gems from heavily used equipment against monsters of equal or greater strength.

60568.「使い込み度とは\n 装備品をどれくらい使い込んだのか\n 知るための 数値です:
An equipment's Usage Level indicates how much you have used a particular piece of equipment in battles.
After battling monsters of an equal or greater challenge to you, your equipment may sparkle, signifying its Usage Level has increased.
Once the Usage Level reaches 100, you will be able to extract Sweat & Tears Gems from it.
If you want to see an equipment's current Usage Level, you can view by examining its details.

60569.「これは 装備すれば\n 戦いのときに どうぐとして使っても\n 効果がある物で:

item in battle to activate its special effect.

121186.「装備品の 装備可能レベルが高いほど\n また 錬金効果が たくさんついているほ:
The higher the equipment's required level and the more alchemy effects it has, the more gems that can be extracted.
If the alchemy effects on the equipment are of good quality, the number of gems you can extract will increase even further.
Even if the equipment has a high quality itself, the number of gems will remain the same if it has no alchemy effects.
It's beneficial to add effects to equipment you plan on extracting from, since the amount of gems will increase, adding more value.

121187.「結晶を取りだすとは お使いの装備品から\n 職人仕事で使える新素材 汗と涙の結:
Gem extraction is a service that allows you to extract Sweat & Tears Gems from equipment, which can be used as crafting materials.
However, you may only extract gems from heavily used equipment against monsters of equal or greater strength.

121188.「使い込み度とは\n 装備品をどれくらい使い込んだのか\n 知るための 数値です:
An equipment's Usage Level indicates how much you have used a particular piece of equipment in battles.
After battling monsters of an equal or greater challenge to you, your equipment may sparkle, signifying its Usage Level has increased.
Once the Usage Level reaches 100, you will be able to extract Sweat & Tears Gems from it.
If you want to see an equipment's current Usage Level, you can view by examining its details.

the Sweat & Tears Gem. The equipment itself will disappear, but the Sweat & Tears Gem will carry on the proof of the traveler's battle,
and become the food for the next piece of equipment.

122257.「使い込み度とは 装備品が どれくらい\n 使い込まれたかを 示す数値です。\n:
The degree of use is a number that indicates how much use an item of equipment has been put to. Sometimes, after fighting a monster of
equal or greater strength, your equipment will shine and its usage level will go up. When the usage level reaches 100, you will be able to
retrieve Sweat & Tears Gems from the equipment. You can check the current usage level by looking at the item in detail.
However, please note that some equipment that cannot be crafted by artisans will not increase in usefulness.

122360.「装備品の 装備可能レベルが高いほど\n また 錬金効果が たくさんついているほ:
The higher the equipable level of the equipment and the more alchemical effects it has, the more crystals can be retrieved. If
the alchemy effect is good, the number of crystals that can be retrieved will increase even more. Even if the quality is high, the
number of crystals that can be retrieved will not change if there is no alchemy effect attached. It is more profitable to add alchemy
effects to the equipment you want to take out crystals, because the number of crystals you can take out will increase.

122361.「使い込み度が１００になるほど使い込まれた\n 装備品からは 職人仕事に使える:

the Sweat & Tears Gem. The equipment itself will disappear, but the Sweat & Tears Gem will carry on the proof of the traveler's battle,
and become the food for the next piece of equipment.

122362.「使い込み度とは 装備品が どれくらい\n 使い込まれたかを 示す数値です。\n:

equal or greater strength, your equipment will shine and its usage level will go up. When the usage level reaches 100, you will be able to
retrieve Sweat & Tears Gems from the equipment. You can check the current usage level by looking at the item in detail.
However, please note that some equipment that cannot be crafted by artisans will not increase in usefulness.

129914.「レベルが４０以上になった 占い師には\n タロット合成を 伝授しているんだ。\:
We teach fortune tellers who have reached level 40 or above the ability to synthesize Tarot, which allows them to create a new Tarot
from the two Tarots they have. By synthesizing Tarot, the rank of the Tarot is raised, the monster becomes more powerful, and the effect
of the monster is strengthened. Arcana is inherited from the material. The effect of using Arcana changes its power depending on
whether the rank is A or higher or not. And one more thing. The rank S, which can be made by collecting two rank A Tarot and combining
them, is also a Mar Honeyce. When you have three Rank S Tarots of the same monster in your hand, they have an aura that makes them
more powerful than usual. There are rumors that there are even higher ranks than Rank S, but I don't know much about them... There is a
book about Tarot synthesis on the bookshelf near the Tarot Table, so you might want to read it if you are interested.

129916.「占い師は バトル中に\n 『タロット』を 使うことができるんだ。\n いくら使:
The fortune teller can use Tarot in battle, and no matter how many Tarot he uses, he will never run out. The number of Tarot that can be
used in battle is 20, and these 20 Tarot are called the "deck". During a battle, you can only use 4 Tarot cards from your deck, chosen
by luck. If you use them, the next Tarot will be added to your deck. If you want to make a deck or check your Tarot, you can use the
"Monster Tarot" command from the "item" menu. There are 22 types of Monster Tarot, called Arcana, such as justice and magician, which
have different effects when used. The monsters on the Tarot have special effects that differ from those of the Arcana. The strength of
the fortune teller lies in the deck. Get a new Tarot and create your own unique and powerful deck.

129918.「モンスタータロットの入手方法は ふたつ。\n まずひとつが ここ タロット屋で:
There are two ways to get Monster Tarot. The first is to buy a Tarot Pack here at the Tarot Shop. If you want more Tarot, you can get a
Tarot Medal. If you win the battle against the Maze Boss by offering the Tarot Medal in a certain labyrinth, you may get a rare
TarotPack as well. You can challenge the battle of the Lord in any location, so if you want to get various Tarot, you should try it
again and again. Arcana Divination is also a good way to collect Tarot Medals. If you put Tarot Medal Fragment into Alchemy Pot, you can
make Tarot Medal. However, I hear that the Maze Boss is a powerful opponent. If you want to challenge him as a fortune teller, you
should go there after gaining experience.

269161.「結晶を取りだすとは お使いの装備品から\n 職人仕事で使える新素材 汗と涙の結:
Gem extraction is a service that allows you to extract Sweat & Tears Gems from equipment, which can be used as crafting materials.
However, you may only extract gems from heavily used equipment against monsters of equal or greater strength.

269162.「使い込み度とは\n 装備品をどれくらい使い込んだのか\n 知るための 数値です:
An equipment's Usage Level indicates how much you have used a particular piece of equipment in battles.
After battling monsters of an equal or greater challenge to you, your equipment may sparkle, signifying its Usage Level has increased.
Once the Usage Level reaches 100, you will be able to extract Sweat & Tears Gems from it.
If you want to see an equipment's current Usage Level, you can view by examining its details.

269163.「装備品の 装備可能レベルが高いほど\n また 錬金効果が たくさんついているほ:
The higher the equipment's required level and the more alchemy effects it has, the more gems that can be extracted.
If the alchemy effects on the equipment are of good quality, the number of gems you can extract will increase even further.
Even if the equipment has a high quality itself, the number of gems will remain the same if it has no alchemy effects.
It's beneficial to add effects to equipment you plan on extracting from, since the amount of gems will increase, adding more value.

271841.「使い込み度が ５０以上になるほど使い込まれた\n 装備品は 職人仕事に使える:
Equipment that has been used more than 50 times will yield special materials that can be used for craftsmanship. That is the Sweat &
Tears Gem. The equipment itself will be gone, but the Sweat & Tears Gem will contain the proof that the travelers fought for it, and it
will be used to make the next piece of equipment.

271842.「使い込み度とは 装備品が どれくらい\n 使い込まれたかを 示す数値だね。\n:
The degree of use is a number that indicates how much use a piece of equipment has been put to. Sometimes, after fighting a monster of
equal or greater strength, your equipment will shine and its usage level will go up. When you have 50 or more uses for a piece of equipment,
you will be able to retrieve a Sweat & Tears Gem from it. You can check the current usage level by looking at the item in detail.
However, please note that some equipment that cannot be made by artisans will not have their usability level increased.

271843.「使い込み度が １００に近ければ近いほど\n 多くの結晶を取りだせるんだ。\n:
The closer to 100 you use your equipment, the more crystals you can retrieve. 50 and 100 are almost double the amount of crystals. Also,
the higher the equipable level of the equipment, the more alchemical effects are attached, the more crystals can be retrieved.
And if the alchemy effect is good, the number of crystals that can be retrieved will increase even more. Even if the quality is
high, if there is no alchemy effect attached, the number of crystals that can be retrieved will remain the same. Therefore, it is more
profitable to add alchemical effects to equipment from which you want to extract crystals, because the number of crystals you
can extract will increase. By the way, the number of times you can take out crystals from your equipment is limited to 10 times per day.
Any crystals not taken out that day will be carried over to the next day, up to a maximum of 250 crystals. I apologize for the
inconvenience, but I would appreciate your cooperation.

285822.「使い込み度とは 装備品が どれくらい\n 使い込まれたかを 示す数値です。\n:
The degree of use is a number that indicates how much use an item of equipment has been put to. Sometimes, after fighting a monster of
equal or greater strength, you will see your equipment glinting and its usage level will go up. When you have 50 or more uses for a piece
of equipment, you will be able to retrieve a Sweat & Tears Gem from it. You can check the current usage level by looking at the item in
detail. However, please note that some equipment that cannot be made by artisans will not have their usability level increased.

the higher the equipable level of the equipment, the more alchemical effects it has, the more crystals can be retrieved. If the
alchemy effect is good, the number of crystals you can take out will increase even more. Even if the quality is high, the number of crystals
that can be retrieved will not change if there is no alchemy effect attached. It is better to add alchemy effects to equipment from which
you want to take out crystals to increase the number of crystals you can take out and get more profit. The number of times crystals can
be taken out from a piece of equipment is limited to 10 times per day. Any crystals not taken out that day will be carried over to the
next day, but the maximum carryover will be 250 crystals. We apologize for the inconvenience and ask for your cooperation.

294308.「使い込み度とは\n 装備品をどれくらい使い込んだのか\n 知るための 数値です:
An equipment's Usage Level indicates how much you have used a particular piece of equipment in battles.
After battling monsters of an equal or greater challenge to you, your equipment may sparkle, signifying its Usage Level has increased.
Once the Usage Level reaches 100, you will be able to extract Sweat & Tears Gems from it.
If you want to see an equipment's current Usage Level, you can view by examining its details.

Even if the equipment has a high quality itself, the number of gems will remain the same if it has no alchemy effects.

301885.「使い込み度とは\n 装備品をどれくらい使い込んだのか\n 知るための 数値です:
An equipment's Usage Level indicates how much you have used a particular piece of equipment in battles.
After battling monsters of an equal or greater challenge to you, your equipment may sparkle, signifying its Usage Level has increased.
Once the Usage Level reaches 100, you will be able to extract Sweat & Tears Gems from it.
If you want to see an equipment's current Usage Level, you can view by examining its details.

If the alchemy effects on the equipment are of good quality, the number of gems you can extract will increase even further.
Even if the equipment has a high quality itself, the number of gems will remain the same if it has no alchemy effects.
It's beneficial to add effects to equipment you plan on extracting from, since the amount of gems will increase, adding more value.
